# Cursor Rules — Choice Credit and Rental Solutions

## Architecture Is Locked

This project uses a fixed production stack. Do not migrate or replace any part of it.

### Stack (non-negotiable)
- Database: Supabase PostgreSQL
- Auth: Supabase Auth
- Storage: Supabase Storage
- Email: Google Apps Script
- Deployment: Cloudflare Pages
- Dev environment: Replit (code editor only — not production)

### Forbidden Actions
- Do NOT replace Supabase with any other database
- Do NOT replace Supabase Auth with Replit Auth, Clerk, or anything else
- Do NOT add @replit/database or @replit/object-storage
- Do NOT replace Google Apps Script email
- Do NOT change the deployment target

### Key Files (do not replace these)
- artifacts/api-server/src/lib/supabase.ts
- artifacts/api-server/src/lib/auth-middleware.ts
- artifacts/choice-credit/src/lib/supabase.ts
- artifacts/choice-credit/src/lib/auth.tsx

### What Is Safe
- New routes in artifacts/api-server/src/routes/
- New pages/components in artifacts/choice-credit/src/
- OpenAPI spec changes in lib/api-spec/openapi.yaml (run codegen after)
- UI and feature work using existing Supabase tables

See ARCHITECTURE.md for the full specification.
